NOTICE: AI Model Licenses

This project integrates AI models with various open-source licenses:

- Apache 2.0: Qwen models, Gemma 4 models, Mistral models, and others
- MIT: GLM-5.1, DeepSeek V3.2, Phi models, and others
- Llama Community License: Llama 4 models (700M MAU restriction)
- Gemma Terms of Use: Gemma models
- Custom permissive licenses: Various model-specific licenses

See docs/LICENSE-MODELS.md for complete model license information.

---

NOTICE: Media Tools and Libraries

This project uses media processing tools with LGPL 2.1+ licenses
via dynamic linking only:

- FFmpeg (LGPL 2.1+, no GPL codecs)
- libvips (LGPL 2.1+)
- ImageMagick (Apache-style license, no GPL delegates)
- PDFium (BSD-3-Clause)
- LibreOffice (MPL 2.0)

See docs/LICENSE-MEDIA.md for complete media toolchain license information.

---

NOTICE: GPL-Free Guarantee

All runtime components use permissive licenses. No GPL dependencies
are included in the runtime execution path.

Flagged components (optional):
- diffusion-small: AGPL (Stable Diffusion)
- index: SSPL (FalkorDB)

These components are clearly flagged and are optional add-ons.
